00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:51,840
We

292
00:20:51,840 --> 00:20:53,310
have worked together in the Wu family

293
00:20:53,310 --> 00:20:55,470
for so many years now.

294
00:20:56,760 --> 00:20:59,950
Have I ever left anyone out
when money's on the table?

295
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:02,710
That's true.

296
00:21:04,070 --> 00:21:05,230
The mining business

297
00:21:06,120 --> 00:21:07,790
will only get better from here.

298
00:21:08,920 --> 00:21:11,470
As your fellow, let me say this.

299
00:21:12,310 --> 00:21:13,710
I hope from now on,

300
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:16,870
