361
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:42,440
Isn't that right?

362
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:44,950
Yeah, that's right.

363
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:47,470
My dear Chairman,

364
00:23:48,870 --> 00:23:49,870
here's the fact.

365
00:23:51,150 --> 00:23:52,440
The company has money.

366
00:23:52,840 --> 00:23:54,150
You love cars, don't you?

367
00:23:54,950 --> 00:23:55,870
Go have your fun.

368
00:23:56,870 --> 00:23:58,440
Champagne, pretty ladies,

369
00:23:58,470 --> 00:23:59,390
and the yacht.

370
00:23:59,390 --> 00:24:00,870
