371
00:24:00,870 --> 00:24:03,200
So why bother handling business with us?

372
00:24:03,710 --> 00:24:04,550
Besides,

373
00:24:05,760 --> 00:24:07,040
haven't you all noticed?

374
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:08,360
Our Chairman

375
00:24:08,790 --> 00:24:09,710
has got

376
00:24:09,710 --> 00:24:11,390
an artistic vibe.

377
00:24:12,040 --> 00:24:13,070
Just look at that hair.

378
00:24:13,470 --> 00:24:14,280
Handsome.

379
00:24:14,950 --> 00:24:17,040
Honestly, he's no worse than

380
00:24:17,190 --> 00:24:18,280
those small stars out there.

381
00:24:19,040 --> 00:24:20,120
Let's drop it.

382
00:24:21,150 --> 00:24:21,950
That's enough.

383
00:24:22,230 --> 00:24:23,920
Everyone, please don't misunderstand.

384
00:24:24,230 --> 00:24:25,550
Uncle Cheng, don't get me wrong.

385
00:24:25,760 --> 00:24:26,630
I'm not here

386
00:24:26,630 --> 00:24:28,840
to argue or anything like that.

387
00:24:28,840 --> 00:24:31,230
