388
00:24:32,200 --> 00:24:34,710
Your previous comments about me
were all true.

389
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:36,760
Like saying I'm unreliable,

390
00:24:36,760 --> 00:24:37,630
not skilled enough,

391
00:24:37,630 --> 00:24:38,600
or lack perspective.

392
00:24:38,920 --> 00:24:40,520
Honestly, I think you're right.

393
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:43,870
About my hair,

394
00:24:43,870 --> 00:24:45,630
you said it hurt the company's image,

395
00:24:45,690 --> 00:24:46,360
and told me to cut it.

396
00:24:46,360 --> 00:24:47,440
But I didn't.

397
00:24:48,390 --> 00:24:49,390
I was wrong.

398
00:24:50,120 --> 00:24:51,310
So today I'm here

399
00:24:51,520 --> 00:24:52,840
just to talk with you

400
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:54,950
and with everyone else here.

401
00:24:55,390 --> 00:24:56,440
Let me say something.

402
00:25:31,680 --> 00:25:33,760
Everyone here
built the business with my dad.

403
00:25:35,310 --> 00:25:37,200
You watched the company
grow from nothing.

404
00:25:40,230 --> 00:25:41,520
You also watched me grow up.

405
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:45,840
Before my dad passed, he told me

406
00:25:46,900 --> 00:25:48,550
that the company was like
his second son,

407
00:25:49,750 --> 00:25:50,840
three years younger than me.

408
00:25:52,430 --> 00:25:53,440
So I'm the older brother.

409
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:54,520
I have to take care of him.

410
00:25:57,440 --> 00:25:58,630
But I ended up losing it.

411
00:26:08,070 --> 00:26:10,280
Now, do I look like a chairman to you?

412
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:23,550
I remember, back when we had nothing,

413
00:26:23,550 --> 00:26:25,470
you all used to come over to our place.

414
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:27,310
You'd sit and talk all night long.

415
00:26:27,800 --> 00:26:29,310
Talking about creativity and contracts.

416
00:26:29,390 --> 00:26:30,230
I was too young

417
00:26:30,230 --> 00:26:31,150
to understand that.

418
00:26:32,440 --> 00:26:34,120
My dad would drink with you guys,

419
00:26:34,120 --> 00:26:35,070
one case after another.

420
00:26:37,840 --> 00:26:38,520
You talked about

421
00:26:38,520 --> 00:26:41,520
dreams, life, and making money.

422
00:26:46,120 --> 00:26:46,950
You want to get rich.

423
00:26:46,950 --> 00:26:48,120
I have no reason to stop you.

424
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:51,950
If you say I'm not capable,
I accept that.

425
00:26:54,950 --> 00:26:57,470
I just want to implore you

426
00:26:58,630 --> 00:27:00,790
to give me a hand

427
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:03,390
for the old times' sake.

428
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:28,280
Ke,

429
00:27:28,280 --> 00:27:30,440
you signed the Stock Transfer Agreement.

430
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:32,230
You can't blame anyone else.

431
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:34,470
Business is like a battlefield.

432
00:27:34,760 --> 00:27:35,840
There are no friends,

433
00:27:35,840 --> 00:27:36,870
only interests.

434
00:27:38,390 --> 00:27:39,200
This is something

435
00:27:40,790 --> 00:27:42,200
we all understand.

436
00:27:42,710 --> 00:27:45,230
The Zhao family knows it too.

437
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:48,470
Uncle Cheng,

438
00:27:49,840 --> 00:27:51,310
I made two mistakes.

439
00:27:54,440 --> 00:27:55,710
First, I trusted you.

440
00:27:57,360 --> 00:27:58,710
Second, I trusted the Zhao family.

441
00:28:03,870 --> 00:28:04,760
You're right.

442
00:28:06,550 --> 00:28:07,520
It's my fault.

443
00:28:11,390 --> 00:28:12,120
No hidden tricks.

444
00:28:12,120 --> 00:28:13,360
There's no comeback for me.

445
00:28:16,030 --> 00:28:17,070
But I've got my conscience

446
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:21,120
and my pride.

447
00:28:26,360 --> 00:28:27,520
Remember this.

448
00:28:28,280 --> 00:28:29,920
No matter what happens next,

449
00:28:31,950 --> 00:28:33,630
my dad built this company.

450
00:28:35,630 --> 00:28:36,550
His last name is Wu,

451
00:28:38,790 --> 00:28:39,600
not Zhao.

452
00:29:23,070 --> 00:29:23,470
Yes.

453
00:29:24,760 --> 00:29:25,710
Everything's settled.

454
00:29:28,310 --> 00:29:30,150
Jinhai's people didn't notice, right?

455
00:29:32,550 --> 00:29:35,310
Our chairman has ties
to the Zhao family,

456
00:29:35,710 --> 00:29:36,920
so they won't catch on.

457
00:29:37,680 --> 00:29:39,550
Good. Nicely done.

458
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:41,920
Mr. Wei,

459
00:29:43,440 --> 00:29:45,390
