460
00:29:45,950 --> 00:29:48,550
Aren't we doing this
for Boss Wei's revenge?

461
00:29:49,120 --> 00:29:50,600
But why did you hand the mining site

462
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:53,950
over to Zhao Xin?

463
00:29:55,310 --> 00:29:57,070
There are secrets in the mining site.

464
00:29:57,360 --> 00:29:59,550
Zhao Xin just got his ticket in.

465
00:30:00,630 --> 00:30:03,280
I used Li Group's bid as a cover,

466
00:30:03,470 --> 00:30:04,840
