It's nothing.

475
00:30:38,150 --> 00:30:39,550
I had too many drinks tonight.

476
00:30:40,870 --> 00:30:41,680
Feeling a bit tired.

477
00:30:42,550 --> 00:30:45,600
I keep thinking back
to when I met Boss Wei.

478
00:30:46,710 --> 00:30:48,000
When I had nowhere to go,

479
00:30:48,870 --> 00:30:49,870
didn't know a thing,

480
00:30:50,870 --> 00:30:52,630
he still kept me around.

481
00:30:54,950 --> 00:30:56,680
You know, such a good person.

482
00:30:57,760 --> 00:31:00,920
It's a shame things he ended that way.

483
00:31:02,230 --> 00:31:03,040
Uncle Cheng,

484
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:04,950
at your age,

485
00:31:06,200 --> 00:31:07,680
