486
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:09,040
Take care of yourself.

487
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:11,840
We've got big plans ahead.

488
00:31:13,360 --> 00:31:14,390
Our game

489
00:31:17,390 --> 00:31:18,710
